{"tid":638435,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"論marvel成功之處 獨立電影唔係主因","createTime":"2018-04-22T17:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:30:09.000Z","uid":23125,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0185db7da99950cadb241e6344a9ff7b16f8f2bd","tid":638435,"uid":23125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"至少我認為獨立電影唔係主因<br />\n<br />\nMarvel最成功既兩部電影 Ironman 同 avengers1<br />\nIronman成功係因為ironman套甲係英雄片比到觀眾好大新鮮感，科技感十足係個陣啲確少電影有呢感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於avengers1既成功就仲簡單，當時佢地promote avengers1個陣係標明史上第一次最強英雄集結，咁已經吸引左一啲平時唔睇英雄片既人都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而先出獨立電影係其次既成功因素<br />\n<br />\n而DC失敗既原因係 英雄集結既先河已經比marvel早一步做先，仲有marvel每一套戲都連繫住infinity war，DC就一啲連貫性都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMarvel既infinity stone由phase1開始介紹 以infinity stone同Thanos連繫10幾套電影，而DC 既mother box 係由JL介紹 仲要完左成場戲都唔知mother box有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我覺得DC失敗既原因係冇左DC版既infinity stone同Thanos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9690ce992b117d9531ae92f47bc37fe4bfad37f9","tid":638435,"uid":77788,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2e19f89139768118988deff0ebc670e12a4ddbe","tid":638435,"uid":86587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩者，一句講哂，DC電影拍得差咪無人睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f167a15926d7a5aabaf97e54a1910356f526477","tid":638435,"uid":23125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2e19f89139768118988deff0ebc670e12a4ddbe","tid":638435,"uid":86587,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩者，一句講哂，DC電影拍得差咪無人